title: How to Quiff | AXE |  Instagroom
description:
This is how Jarno owns the heck out of his nose: with a tall quiff.

THE TOOLS:
AXE Signature Clean Cut Look Classic Pomade 

THE STEPS:
1. Rub pomade on hands
2. Rake way back
3. Squeeze into hair for texture
4. Deal with the sides

Subscribe to the AXE channel for more grooming tips.

asset.author: AXE

transcripts: One thing I like about the quiff is that it is really deliberate. First I take the pomade in my hand and rub it all together. Rake back my hair. Grab it a little bit to add a bit of texture and make it a bit more personal and deal with the sides, ‘cause otherwise they’ll pop out like a mad scientist.
